<br>
As the assigned Ambassador to Benevolent Order from the allied guild of the Mystic Entity....I would like to say Hello and welcome you to a wonderful guild.<br>
<br>
The FAMILY you have joined welcomes you with open arms and I am glad to see that you have chosen B.O. as your new home amongst the the wilds of Norrath.<br>
<br>
Per our alliance, the membership of Mystic Entity will lend a hand of assistance when we can to our B.O. friends - so please do not be afraid to do a /who all Mystic when you are on if you need something.  PLEASE - if you do have a question, concern or need some help with something.....if you see that I, Todak Honorblade, am in game....send your tells to me first so that I may pass along your request if I cannot assist myself.  IN FACT.....add "Todak" to all your friends lists if you would like.<br>
<br>
If you look to your "events planning" section of this board, you will see many Mystic Entity raids and events posted to that section of the B.O. board's with links to the main post on our boards.  As a member of the Benevolent Order and as laid out in the alliance between our two guilds, being a member of B.O. provides you with admittance to all raids scheduled by my guild.  Please be aware though that raid spots are filled on a first come/first serve basis and signing up on the raid/event post on the Mystic Entity boards is the only SURE way to get a spot.<br>
<br>
*the only events you will not be allowed to attend are those that will be "mystic entity members only".<br>
<br>
SO.....once again, welcome to a great and honorable guild.  Act justly, bravely and with truth in your hearts.  And of course....say Hello to your Mystic Entity friends when you see us !<br>
<br>
